y,A-Flohr,S URS-ch16 Moscow 1948 (11)} f5 {[%csl Rc8];½-½ Inarkiev,E (2688)-Ding,L (2730) Moscow Petrosian Memorial 2014 (5)} 40. Kg1 $142 Qe1+ 41. Rf1 Qb4 42. Rxf5 Qxa4 43. Bxa6 Qxa6 44. Rf3 Qb6+ 45. Kh1 Qb1+ 46. Kh2 Qxc2 47. Rf1 Qe2 48. Rf3 Qe1 49. Rf5 Kg7 50. Rf3 Kg6 51. Rd3 Kf5 52. Rf3+ Ke4 53. Rf7 Qg3+ 54. Kh1 Qe1+ 55. Kh2 Kd5 56. Rf3 Ke6 57. Rd3 Kf5 58. Rf3+ Kg5 59. Rf7 Qe5+ 60. Kh1 Qd4 61. Rf3 Qa1+ 62. Kh2 Qd1 63. Rf7 Kg6 64. Rf3 Qb1 65. Rf2 Qb8+ 66. Kh1 Qe5 67. Rf3 Qa1+ 68. Kh2 Qe1 69. Rd3 Kf6 {Dominguez Perez,L (2726)-Wojtaszek,R (2744) Beijing 2014 ½-½} 70. Rf3+ Ke7 {La grande ligne} 71. Rf5 Qe6 72. Rf3 Qe5+ {L'alternative} 73. Kh1 Qa1+ 74. Kh2 Qc1 75. Rf5 Qc7+ 76. Kh1 Ke6 77. Rf3 Qe5 78. Kg1 Qe1+ 79. Kh2 Qe5+ 80. Kh1 Qa1+ 81. Kh2 Qe1 82. Rd3 Kf5 83. Rf3+ Kg6 84. Rd3 Qe7 85. Rf3 Qd6+ 86. Kh1 Qd1+ 87. Kh2 Qe2 88. Kh1 Qe1+ 89. Kh2 Qd1 90. Rf2 Qd6+ 91. Kh1 Qd1+ 92. Kh2 Qe1 93. Rf3 Qb1 94. Rf2 Qb8+ 95. Kh1 h5 96. Rf3 Qb1+ 97. Kh2 Qb6 98. Kh1 Qd6 99. Kg1 Qe5 100. Kh1 Qa1+ 101. Kh2 Qe1 102. Rd3 Kf5 103. Rf3+ Ke6 104. Rd3 Qe5+ 105. Kh1 Qa1+ 106. Kh2 Qa7 107. Rf3 Qb8+ 108. Kh1 Qb1+ 109. Kh2 Qc1 110. Rd3 Ke5 111. Rf3 Qc7 112. Kg1 Ke4 113. Kh1 Qc1+ 114. Kh2 Qe1 115. Rb3 Qd1 116. Rf3 Qxf3 117. gxf3+ Kxf3 118. Kg1 Kg3 119. Kh1 Kxh3 120. Kg1 Kg3 121. Kh1 Kf3 122. Kh2 Kf4 123. Kh3 Kg5 124. Kh2 Kg4 125. Kg2 h3+ 126. Kh2 Kh4 127. Kg1 Kg3 128. Kh1 Kg4 129. Kh2 Kh4 130. Kg1 Kg3 131. Kh1 h4 132. Kg1 Kf3 133. Kh2 Kg4 134. Kh1 Kg3 135. Kg1 h2+ 136. Kh1 Kf3 137. Kxh2 Kg4 138. Kg2 Kf4 139. Kh3 Kg5 140. Kg2 Kg4 141. Kh2 h3 142. Kg1 Kg3 143. Kh1 Kf3 144. Kh2 Kg4 145. Kh1 Kg3 146. Kg1 h2+ 147. Kh1 Kh3 1/2-1/2


