{[%evp 0,77,19,38,18,26,21,2,3,0,0,0,8,1,1,-2,-21,5,-4,4,-12,-20,-30,-38,3,-26,-18,-29,-36,-27,-29,-22,-1,-8,3,-9,21,0,7,0,8,0,10,-5,-38,-33,-23,-112,-121,-115,-139,-156,-140,-162,-110,-98,-62,-105,-109,-57,498,654,654,654,654,717,718,718,718,758,1516,2095,29999,29998,29999,29996,29997,29990,29997,827]} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 exd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nxc6 bxc6 6. Bd3 d5 7. exd5 cxd5 8. O-O Be7 9. c4 d4 (9... O-O 10. Nc3 (10. cxd5 Bb7 11. Nc3 Nxd5 12. Bd2 Nxc3 13. Bxc3 Bf6 14. Bxf6 Qxf6 15. Qc2 g6 16. Qxc7 Qxb2 17. Rab1 Qd4 18. Rfd1 Bd5 19. Bxg6 Qc4 20. Bxh7+ Kxh7 21. Qe5 Be6 22. Rd4 Qc2 23. Re1 Kg6 24. h3 Rae8 25. Rh4 Bf5 26. Qg3+ Kf6 27. Qd6+ Be6 28. Re3 {1-0 (28) Xiong,J (2712)-Sethuraman,S (2634) Saint Louis 2019}) 10... Bb7 (10... d4 11. Ne4) 11. Qf3 Rb8 12. Nxd5 Nxd5 13. Be4 c6 14. cxd5 cxd5 15. Bd3 Ba8 16. b3 d4 17. Qg3 Bd6 18. Bf4 Bxf4 19. Qxf4 Qd5 20. f3 Rbe8 21. Rfd1 Rd8 22. Rac1 Qa5 23. Rc2 g6 24. Qc7 Qg5 25. Qg3 Qf6 26. Rc7 Qb6 27. h4 Rc8 28. Rdc1 Rxc7 29. Rxc7 h5 30. Qf4 Bd5 31. Kh2 Rd8 32. Qe5 a5 33. Qe7 Rf8 34. Rd7 Be6 35. Qd6 Qb4 36. Qxb4 axb4 37. Rxd4 Ra8 38. Bb1 Rb8 39. Kg3 Kg7 40. Kf4 Kf6 41. g4 hxg4 42. fxg4 Ke7 43. h5 gxh5 44. gxh5 Rg8 45. Bf5 Rg2 46. Bxe6 Kxe6 47. Rxb4 Rxa2 48. Rb6+ Ke7 49. b4 Rh2 50. h6 {1-0 (50) Shankland,S (2709)-So,W (2772) Saint Louis 2021}) 10. Bg5 O-O 11. Nd2 Bg4 12. Nf3 h6 13. Bxf6 Bxf6 14. h3 Be6 15. b4 a5 16. b5 Qd6 17. Re1 Rad8 18. Qc2 Qa3 19. Rac1 Rfe8 20. Re2 Bc8 21. Rce1 Rxe2 22. Qxe2 g6 23. Nd2 Qxa2 24. Qd1 Bb7 25. c5 Bd5 26. Ne4 Be7 27. Qf3 Bxe4 28. Rxe4 Bxc5 29. Qf6 Rf8 30. Rg4 Re8 31. Bxg6 Re1+ 32. Kh2 Bd6+ 33. f4 Kf8 34. Bh7 Ke8 35. Rg8+ Kd7 36. Bf5+ Re6 37. Qxf7+ Be7 38. Bxe6+ Qxe6 39. Rd8+ 1-0


