1. d4 {Paunovic,Tomislav} d5 2. c4 c6 3. Nf3 Nf6 4. Nc3 a6 5. e3 e6 6. Bd3 dxc4 7. Bxc4 b5 8. Be2 c5 9. O-O Bb7 10. dxc5 Qxd1 (10... Bxc5) 11. Rxd1 Bxc5 12. Nd2 (12. a3 {(Paunovic,Tomislav) - 13/537}) 12... Nbd7 13. Nb3 {[%csl Rc5][%cal Yb3a5]} Bb4 $1 (13... Bb6 {is covered in Bischoff-Stohl, as well as other alternatives.}) 14. Bd2 O-O 15. f3 $5 {Paunovic,Tomislav: 'N'} (15. a3 Nc5 $1 16. Nc1 (16. Nd4 Bxc3 17. Bxc3 Rfc8 18. Bb4 Na4 19. b3 Nc3 20. Bxc3 Rxc3 $11) 16... Bxc3 17. Bxc3 Rfc8 (17... Na4 $6 18. Bd4 $1 $14) 18. Bd4 Bd5 19. f3 Bc4 20. Kf2 Bxe2 21. Kxe2 Nd5 22. Rd2 f6 23. Bxc5 Rxc5 24. Nd3 Rc7 25. a4 bxa4 26. Rxa4 {Kramnik-Tomashevsky, Moscow 2012; and although White won a nice game Black could have equalised here with} a5 $1 27. e4 Nb6 28. Ra1 a4 $11) (15. a4 bxa4 16. Nxa4 (16. Rxa4 a5 17. Raa1 Rfd8 $1 (17... Rfc8 $6 18. Nb5 {[%csl Ra5]} Rc2 (18... Bxd2 19. Rxd2 a4 20. N3d4 $14 {[%cal Yf2f3]}) 19. N5d4 $1 (19. Bxb4 axb4 20. Rxa8+ Bxa8 21. Rd2 Rxd2 22. Nxd2 Ne4 $11 {Shomoev-Smirnov, Taganrog 2015}) 19... Rxb2 20. Bc1 Rxe2 21. Nxe2 $14 {and Black doesn't have sufficient compensation for the exchange.}) 18. Be1 (18. Nb5 Bxd2 19. Rxd2 (19. Nxd2 Nb6 $11 {[%cal Ya5a4]}) 19... a4 20. N3d4 Nc5 $11) 18... Rdc8 19. Nd4 Nb6 {½-½ Vidit-Sengupta, Dharamshala 2014.}) 16... a5 (16... Bxd2 17. Rxd2 $14 {[%cal Yb3a5]}) 17. Bxb4 axb4 18. Nac5 Bd5 19. f3 Rxa1 20. Rxa1 Rc8 21. Rc1 Bxb3 22. Nxb3 Rxc1+ 23. Nxc1 Nc5 $11 {Topalov-Wang, Stavanger 2013.}) 15... Nc5 16. Nd4 (16. Ne4 Nxb3 17. Bxb4 (17. axb3 Bxd2 18. Nxf6+ gxf6 19. Rxd2 Rfd8 20. Rad1 Rxd2 21. Rxd2 f5 $11 {[%cal Yb7d5]}) 17... Nxa1 18. Nxf6+ gxf6 19. Bxf8 Kxf8 20. Rxa1 Rc8 21. Bd3 $11) 16... Rfc8 (16... Ba5 $5 {Paunovic,Tomislav} 17. Ne4 Bb6 18. Nxc5 (18. Nxf6+ gxf6 19. Rac1 Rfd8 $11) 18... Bxc5 19. a4 Bxd4 $140 20. exd4 Bc6 21. Rdc1 Bd7 22. b3 $36) 17. Ne4 (17. a3 Bxc3 18. bxc3 (18. Bxc3 Na4 $1 $15) 18... Bd5 19. e4 Bb3 20. Nxb3 Nxb3 21. Ra2 Nxd2 22. Raxd2 Kf8 23. c4 bxc4 24. Rc2 Rab8 25. Bxc4 a5 $11) 17... Bxd2 (17... Ncxe4 $6 {Paunovic,Tomislav} 18. Bxb4 Nd5 19. Be1 $14) 18. Nxf6+ gxf6 19. Rxd2 f5 (19... Kf8 20. e4 {Paunovic,Tomislav: ''} Ke7 {[%cal Yc8d8,Ya8c8] is pretty close to equality.}) 20. b3 {Paunovic,Tomislav: ''} Kf8 21. Kf2 Ke7 22. h3 Nd7 (22... h5 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '!?'} 23. h4 $14 {[%csl Rh5]}) 23. g4 (23. a4 $5 {Paunovic,Tomislav}) 23... Nf6 $6 (23... Rc3 $1 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '!?'} 24. gxf5 e5 25. f6+ Nxf6 26. Nf5+ Ke6 $11) 24. gxf5 $2 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '?!'} (24. a4 $1 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '!'} b4 25. a5 $16 {[%csl Rb4][%cal Ya1a4]}) 24... e5 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '!'} 25. Nc2 Rc3 $132 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '!'} 26. Nb4 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '?!'} e4 {Paunovic,Tomislav: '='} 27. Rc2 Rxc2 28. Nxc2 exf3 29. Bxf3 Ne4+ 30. Ke2 Ng3+ 31. Kf2 Ne4+ 32. Ke2 Ng3+ 33. Kf2 1/2-1/2


