1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 c5 4. cxd5 exd5 5. Nf3 Nf6 6. e3 Nc6 7. Be2 cxd4 8. Nxd4 Bc5 9. O-O O-O 10. Nxc6 bxc6 11. b3 Re8 {is the legacy move (11...Qe7). ist old school (11...De7).} 12. Bb2 Bd6 13. Rc1 Bc7 14. Ba3 $146 ({Predecessor:} 14. Bf3 Qd6 15. g3 Bh3 16. Re1 Rad8 17. Qc2 Ba5 18. a3 c5 19. Red1 Bb6 20. Nxd5 Nxd5 21. Rxd5 Qh6 22. Rh5 {1-0 Ozen,B (2369)-Kapitanchuk,T (2346) Titled Tuesday intern op 06th July blitz 2021 (6)}) 14... Bf5 15. Na4 Qd7 16. Nc5 Qd6 17. g3 Bh3 18. Re1 Ba5 19. b4 Bb6 20. Bb2 Rab8 21. Bd4 Qe7 22. Bd3 h6 23. Qf3 Ne4 24. a3 Bxc5 25. Bxc5 Qe6 26. Qe2 Rb7 27. Bd4 Ng5 28. f3 Bf5 29. Ba6 Rd7 30. h4 Nh3+ 31. Kg2 h5 32. Bd3 g5 33. Rxc6 Qxc6 34. Bxf5 Rc7 35. Kxh3 Qa4 36. hxg5 Rc4 37. f4 Rxd4 38. Qxh5 Rd2 39. Qh7+ Kf8 40. Qh6+ Ke7 41. Qf6+ Kf8 42. g6 1-0


