{[%evp 0,69,19,-12,7,-3,4,4,4,-19,-5,1,7,7,10,-19,-6,-9,44,34,27,-14,34,30,62,62,69,73,58,-13,21,35,55,55,55,60,161,118,113,172,168,44,160,104,146,88,124,-17,-2,17,97,-42,0,0,-73,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,118,0,0,-57,370,330,1034,1177,29997,29998]} 1. c4 e6 2. Nc3 d5 3. d4 Nf6 4. cxd5 exd5 5. Bg5 Bb4 6. e3 h6 7. Bh4 g5 8. Bg3 Ne4 9. Nge2 h5 10. h4 Nxg3 11. Nxg3 gxh4 12. Nxh5 c6 (12... Qg5 13. Qa4+ (13. Nf4 c6 14. Qa4 Bxc3+ $6 (14... Bd6 $1 15. Nfxd5 Nd7 16. Nf4 (16. Nb4 Nb6 17. Qb3 Be6 18. d5 Nxd5 19. Nbxd5 O-O-O 20. Ne4 Qxd5 21. Qxd5 Bxd5 22. Nxd6+ Rxd6 $11) 16... Bxf4 17. exf4 Qxf4 $11) 15. bxc3 $14 {1-0 (64) So,W (2776)-Gavrilescu,D (2518) Warsaw 2022}) 13... Nc6 14. Nf4 Rh6 15. Qb5 Bf5 16. Nfxd5 a6 17. Qa4 $14 {1-0 (39) Nepomniachtchi,I (2784)-Matlakov,M (2698) Moscow 2020}) 13. a3 Bd6 (13... Bxc3+ 14. bxc3 Qg5 15. Nf4 $14) 14. g3 (14. f4 Nd7 15. g4 (15. Ng7+ Kf8 16. Nf5 Nf6 (16... Nb6 17. Nxd6 Qxd6 18. Qf3 Qg6 19. Qf2 Qf6 $11 {0-1 (53) Alonso Rosell,A (2564)-Santos Latasa,J (2656) Ciutadella de Menorca 2022}) 17. Nxh4 Rh6 $44 {½-½ (52) Strikovic,A (2450)-Carbone,D (2350) Montevideo 2023}) 15... Nf6 (15... hxg3 16. Ng7+ Ke7 17. Nf5+ Ke6 18. Ng7+ Ke7 19. Nf5+ Ke6 20. Rxh8 Qxh8 21. Qg4 Nf6 22. Qg5 Bd7 $4 (22... Bf8 {would keep Black very much alive.}) 23. Nxd6 $18 {1-0 (25) Lopez Azambuja,N (2225)-Carbone,D (2336) Montevideo 2023}) 16. Rxh4 Nxh5 17. Rxh5 (17. g5 $1 Qe7 18. Kd2 Bf5 19. Rxh5 $16) 17... Rxh5 18. gxh5 Bf5 19. Kd2 $14 {0-1 (47) Yilmaz,M (2621)-Livaic,L (2574) Zagreb 2022}) 14... hxg3 15. Qf3 Be6 (15... gxf2+ $2 16. Kd2 $1 Be6 17. Bh3 {1-0 (17) Faridani,A (2147)-Egan,M (2172) ICCF email 2014}) 16. e4 $1 (16. fxg3 $2 Nd7 17. O-O-O Qg5 18. Be2 O-O-O $17 {0-1 (26) Galaviz Medina,S (2345)-Horvath,D (2505) Cala Gonone 2022}) 16... gxf2+ 17. Kxf2 Nd7 18. exd5 Qb6 $1 (18... cxd5 $2 19. Nxd5 $18) 19. dxe6 fxe6 20. Qe3 (20. Nf6+ Ke7 21. Nxd7 Kxd7 22. Rxh8 Rxh8 23. Ke1 Rf8 24. Qg2 Be7 25. Ne4 Kc8 26. Nc5 Bxc5 27. dxc5 Qxc5 $44 {½-½ (38) Rada,H (2416)-Costachi,M (2239) ICCF email 2017}) 20... O-O-O ({Black has full compensation for the piece after} 20... Qxb2+ 21. Be2 O-O-O) 21. b4 {The position is extremely complicated and not suited for a time trouble in rapid chess.} Rdf8+ 22. Ke2 e5 23. d5 Bc5 24. Qd3 Bxb4 25. Ne4 Nc5 26. Nxc5 Bxc5 27. Rb1 Rf2+ 28. Kd1 Qa5 29. Bh3+ Kb8 30. dxc6 Rd8 31. Rxb7+ Ka8 32. Bd7 Qa4+ 33. Rb3 Bxa3 34. c7 Qxd7 35. cxd8=Q+ 1-0


