 Rxa2+ 43. Kb1 f6 $11) 38... Bxh5 39. Ra5 g5 40. b4 f5 $2 (40... Rcc2 41. b5 Bf3 42. b6 Kg6 43. Bd4 Rc4 44. Bc5 (44. Rd1 h5 $17) 44... f6 $17) 41. Ra7+ Kg6 42. Ra6+ Kh7 43. Rh1 (43. Ra7+ Kg6 $11) 43... f4 44. Bc5 $2 (44. Rxh5 fxe3 45. Rhxh6+ Kg7 46. Rag6+ Kf7 47. Rf6+ Ke7 48. Re6+ Kf7 49. Ref6+ Ke7 $11) 44... Rd8 45. b5 Bf3 (45... Rdd2 $142 46. b6 Bf3 {Diagram [#]} 47. Rxh6+ $1 (47. Rc1 Bb7 48. Ra7 Kg6 49. Bb4 Rb2 50. Bc5 Bd5 $17) 47... Kxh6 48. b7+ Kh5 49. b8=Q Re1+ 50. Qb1 Rxb1+ 51. Kxb1 Be4+ 52. Ka1 g4 $15) 46. Rhxh6+ Kg8 47. Rhg6+ Kh7 48. Rgd6 Rxd6 49. Rxd6 Re5 $11 50. Rd7+ Kg6 51. Rc7 g4 52. b6 g3 53. fxg3 fxg3 54. Bd4 g2 55. Rc1 Re2 56. a3 Rd2 57. Bc5 Bd5 58. Kb1 Be4+ 59. Ka1 Bd5 1/2-1/2


