1. d4 d5 2. c4 dxc4 3. e4 e5 4. Nf3 Bb4+ 5. Bd2 Bxd2+ 6. Qxd2 exd4 7. Qxd4 {7.Nxd4 is the fancy move. 7.Sxd4 ist der angesagte Zug.} (7. Bxc4 $6 c5 $5 8. b4 (8. O-O Nc6 $15) 8... Nf6 (8... Nc6 9. bxc5 Nf6 10. O-O O-O 11. Re1 Bg4 12. e5 Nd7 13. Nxd4 {Djurhuus-Rublevsky, Oakham 1992} Ndxe5 14. Nxc6 Nxc6 $11) 9. bxc5 O-O 10. e5 Nfd7 $15) 7... Nf6 $1 {The best way to equalize.} (7... Qxd4 8. Nxd4 Ne7 (8... Bd7 9. Bxc4 Nc6 10. Nxc6 Bxc6 11. Nc3 $14 {[%csl Rc6][%cal Yf2f3] Duda-Aronian, chess24.com 2022}) (8... Nf6 9. Nc3 O-O 10. Bxc4 $14 c5 $6 11. Nb3 Nbd7 {[%csl Rc8,Rd7]} (11... b6 $2 12. e5 $1 Re8 13. O-O-O Rxe5 14. Rd8+ Re8 15. Rxe8+ Nxe8 16. Bd5 $18) 12. f4 $1 Nb6 13. Be2 Bg4 14. Nxc5 $18 {Shirov-Kashlinskaya, Douglas 2019}) 9. Nc3 a6 10. Bxc4 (10. a4 $6 {Ter Sahakyan-Aronian, Chess.com 2023} c5 11. Nc2 Be6 12. Ne3 Nbc6 $15 {[%csl Gd4][%cal Ye8c8]}) 10... b5 11. Be2 c5 12. Nc2 $5 (12. Nb3 c4 13. Nd4 Nbc6 14. O-O-O Bd7 $1 15. Nxc6 Nxc6 {[%cal Ye8c8]} 16. Rd6 O-O-O $1 17. Rhd1 Kc7 18. f4 Be6 19. e5 Rxd6 20. Rxd6 Rd8 21. Rxd8 Kxd8 $11 {Gukesh-Mamedyarov, Chennai 2022.}) 12... Nbc6 13. O-O-O $14 {[%cal Yd1d2,Yh1d1]}) 8. Qxd8+ (8. Nc3 Be6 {transposes.}) 8... Kxd8 9. Nc3 (9. Bxc4 Nxe4 {[%cal Yh8e8]} 10. Bxf7 (10. Ne5 Re8 11. Nxf7+ Ke7) 10... Nd6 11. Bb3 Re8+ $15) 9... Be6 10. Nd4 (10. Ne5 Nc6 (10... Ke7 11. f4 g6 12. Bxc4 Nbd7 13. Bxe6 fxe6 14. Nd3 $14 {Nikolic-Seirawan, Tilburg 1990}) 11. Nxc6+ (11. Nxc4 Ke7 12. Ne3 Rhd8 13. f4 Kf8 14. Be2 Nd4 $11 {Salov-Nikolic, Reykjavik 1991}) 11... bxc6 12. f4 g6 13. O-O-O+ Ke7 14. Be2 h5 $11 {Timman-Salov, Sanghi Nagar 1994}) (10. Ng5 Nc6 11. Nxe6+ fxe6 12. Bxc4 Ke7 $11 {is also unproblematic for Black in Polgar,Z-Dlugy, Brussels 1987.}) 10... Ke7 (10... Nc6 11. Nxc6+ (11. Nxe6+ fxe6 {see 10.Ng5.}) 11... bxc6 {see 10.Ne5.}) 11. f4 {'N!' A top novelty. Eine Top Neuerung.} ({Predecessor:} 11. Nxe6 fxe6 12. Bxc4 Rd8 (12... Nbd7 13. Be2 c6 14. Kd2 e5 15. Ke3 Nc5 16. h4 Rhd8 17. Rad1 {½-½ (27) Turov,M (2609)-Predojevic,B (2631) Norway 2015}) 13. f3 Nc6 $11 {Karpov-Ivanchuk, Roquebrune 1992.}) 11... Rd8 12. O-O-O c5 13. Nxe6 Rxd1+ 14. Nxd1 fxe6 15. Bxc4 Nc6 16. Re1 Rd8 17. Nc3 Rd4 18. b3 a6 19. e5 Ng4 20. g3 Nb4 21. Kb1 $2 (21. Rd1 g5 $5 $132 (21... Nxh2 $6 22. Be2 $1 {[%csl Rh2]})) 21... b5 22. Be2 Nf2 $2 (22... Ne3 $1 23. Bf3 (23. Bxb5 $2 Nec2 $1 $19 {[%csl Rb5,Re1]}) 23... Rd3 24. Rc1 Ned5 25. Bxd5 exd5 26. a3 Nc6 27. Kc2 c4 28. bxc4 bxc4 $17) 23. a3 Nd5 24. Nxd5+ exd5 25. Kc2 c4 26. bxc4 dxc4 $6 (26... bxc4 $11) 27. Rf1 $1 Ne4 28. Rd1 $1 Rxd1 29. Bxd1 g5 $2 (29... g6 30. Bf3 Nc5 31. Kc3 Ke6 $11) 30. f5 $18 a5 31. f6+ Kf8 32. Bf3 Nc5 33. Kc3 Nd7 34. Kd4 c3 35. Bd1 b4 36. a4 Kf7 37. Bb3+ Kg6 38. Kd5 g4 39. Bc2+ Kf7 40. e6+ Kxf6 41. exd7 Ke7 42. Kc6 1-0


