lins: '?' '?''} d5 $17 {Fernandez,Daniel Howard: 'Sam Collins: '!' '!' Sam Collins: ', threatening ...Bc5+, is easy to miss from a distance.' Sam Collins: ', threatening ...Bc5+, is easy to miss from a distance. Fernandez,D: '''' Fernandez,Daniel Howard: 'Sam Collins: '!' Sam Collins: ', threatening ...Bc5+, is easy to miss from a distance.''}) 14... Nxe4 {[%emt 0:02:56]} 15. f3 {[%emt 0:04:13]} Nef6 {[%emt 0:00:29]} 16. Nxd6+ {[%emt 0:02:09]} Bxd6 {[%emt 0:00:24]} 17. Rxd6 {[%emt 0:00:01]} Ke7 {[%emt 0:02:41]} 18. Rd4 {[%emt 0:14:34]} Ne5 {[%emt 0:05:21] Fernandez,Daniel Howard: 'Sam Collins: 'It's easy to imagine White becoming worse in such an endgame, but Vidit plays accurately and energetically to bring the position to safety.''} 19. Be3 {[%emt 0:00:51]} Nc6 {[%emt 0:06:05]} (19... Nd5 {is a bit more ambitious; Black's minor pieces are probably slightly better placed so he should think about fighting for an advantage.}) 20. Rxd8 {[%emt 0:02:48]} Rxd8 {[%emt 0:00:11]} 21. Bc5+ {[%emt 0:04:35]} Kd7 {[%emt 0:00:57]} 22. Nc4 {[%emt 0:05:54]} Nd5 {[%emt 0:02:13]} 23. a4 {[%emt 0:02:19] Whereas in this version, White' bishop has become active so although Black may still be optically for choice, there decidedly isn't an edge unless White messes up. Fernandez,Daniel Howard: 'Whereas in this version, White' bishop has become active so although Black may still be optically for choice, there decidedly isn't an edge unless White messes up. Sam Collins: 'Fernandez,D: 'Whereas in this version, White' bishop has become active so although Black may still be optically for choice, there decidedly isn't an edge unless White messes up.'''} e5 {[%emt 0:08:33]} 24. a5 {[%emt 0:16:24]} Ke6 {[%emt 0:02:22]} (24... f6 {is more patient and keeps open knight re-routings starting with ...c7, but should objectively also be nothing.}) 25. a6 {[%emt 0:01:10]} bxa6 {[%emt 0:02:47]} 26. Rxa6 {[%emt 0:00:04]} Kd7 {[%emt 0:00:04]} 27. b4 {[%emt 0:07:20] A final simplifying combination. Fernandez,Daniel Howard: 'A final simplifying combination. Sam Collins: 'Fernandez,D: 'A final simplifying combination.'''} Ndxb4 {[%emt 0:01:58]} 28. Bxb4 {[%emt 0:02:33]} Nxb4 {[%emt 0:00:06]} 29. Rd6+ {[%emt 0:01:11]} Ke7 {[%emt 0:00:17]} 30. Rxd8 {[%emt 0:00:01]} Kxd8 {[%emt 0:00:08]} 31. Nxe5 {[%emt 0:00:02]} 1/2-1/2


